"{\"uid\": \"townhall.com-columnists-michaelbrown-2024-07-29-the-olympic-opening-ceremonies-and-why-lgbtq-public-displays-celebrate-perversity-n2642642\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"For the last 20 years, when it comes to LGBTQ+ people and issues, I have followed this simple directive from the Lord: \\\"Reach out and resist,\\\" meaning, \\\"Reach out to the people with compassion; resist the agenda with courage.\\\"\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 226, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last 20 years\", \"from\": 4, \"to\": 21}, {\"ngram\": \"LGBTQ+ people\", \"from\": 40, \"to\": 53}, {\"ngram\": \"issues\", \"from\": 58, \"to\": 64}, {\"ngram\": \"this simple directive\", \"from\": 82, \"to\": 103}, {\"ngram\": \"the Lord\", \"from\": 109, \"to\": 117}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 166, \"to\": 176}, {\"ngram\": \"compassion\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 192}, {\"ngram\": \"the agenda\", \"from\": 201, \"to\": 211}, {\"ngram\": \"courage\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or, put another way (and now in the title of a forthcoming book), we should have hearts of compassion and backbones of steel.\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 352, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another way\", \"from\": 235, \"to\": 246}, {\"ngram\": \"the title\", \"from\": 259, \"to\": 268}, {\"ngram\": \"a forthcoming book\", \"from\": 272, \"to\": 290}, {\"ngram\": \"hearts\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 314}, {\"ngram\": \"compassion\", \"from\": 318, \"to\": 328}, {\"ngram\": \"backbones\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 342}, {\"ngram\": \"steel\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In keeping with that spirit, I do not demonize those who identify as LGBTQ+, as if all of them were devious sexual predators who gloried in BDSM practices and delighted in displays of public perversity.\", \"from\": 354, \"to\": 556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 494, \"end\": 498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BDSM\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2815782043846888e-33, \"text\": \"BDSM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BDSM\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BDSM\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that spirit\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 381}, {\"ngram\": \"LGBTQ+\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 429}, {\"ngram\": \"devious sexual predators\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"displays\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 534}, {\"ngram\": \"public perversity\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why, then, have gay pride events for decades been marked by these very perverse displays?\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gay pride events\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 590}, {\"ngram\": \"decades\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 602}, {\"ngram\": \"these very perverse displays\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 646}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And why were the opening ceremonies of the Olympic games, intended by the planners to draw attention to France's LGBTQ+ community, marked by such perversity?\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 752, \"end\": 758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.7670717448780949, \"rank\": 0.3031927113027359, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremonies\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 683}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic games\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 704}, {\"ngram\": \"the planners\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 730}, {\"ngram\": \"attention\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"such perversity\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 804}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We can put aside for a moment the debate as to just how offensive the ceremonies were, in particular, the degree of intentionality behind the despicable mockery of DaVinci's Last Supper portrait, with a drag queen, wearing a crown, taking the place of Jesus.\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 971, \"end\": 978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8962738556521803e-31, \"text\": \"DaVinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 981, \"end\": 992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Last_Supper\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.926270905710958e-34, \"text\": \"Last Supper\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Last_Supper\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Last_Supper\"}, {\"begin\": 1059, \"end\": 1064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.999990894400145, \"rank\": 9.105682727017886e-06, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 836}, {\"ngram\": \"the debate\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 847}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremonies\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 887}, {\"ngram\": \", in particular, the degree\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 919}, {\"ngram\": \"intentionality\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 937}, {\"ngram\": \"the despicable mockery\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 967}, {\"ngram\": \"a drag queen\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1020}, {\"ngram\": \"a crown\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1037}, {\"ngram\": \"the place\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will say, though, that the ultimate, ironically tone deaf comments have come from those celebrating the \\\"inclusivity\\\" of the event, as if mocking something sacred to Christians was being inclusive to them.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1235, \"end\": 1245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.997742531457315, \"rank\": 0.0022613902931303874, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ultimate, ironically tone deaf comments\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"inclusivity\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1185}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1199}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To quote the Associated Press directly, \\\"In an unprecedented display of inclusivity, drag queens took center stage at the Paris Olympics opening ceremony, showcasing the vibrant and influential role of the French LGBTQ+ community - while also attracting criticism over a tableau reminiscent of 'The Last Supper.'\\\"\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1288, \"end\": 1304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 0.9999990803707669, \"rank\": 9.196300557900673e-07, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}, {\"begin\": 1481, \"end\": 1487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999047494607723, \"rank\": 9.525808942064995e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an unprecedented display\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusivity\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"drag queens\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1371}, {\"ngram\": \"center stage\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1389}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\": \"the vibrant and influential role\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1473}, {\"ngram\": \"criticism\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"a tableau\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1553}, {\"ngram\": \"The Last Supper\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or, as expressed by Paris 2024 spokesperson Anne Descamps, \\\"Clearly there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group.\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1729, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1610, \"end\": 1620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.4380345183721226e-17, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an intention\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1686}, {\"ngram\": \"any religious group\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(The opening ceremony) tried to celebrate community tolerance.\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1792, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(The opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1751}, {\"ngram\": \"community tolerance\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We believe this ambition was achieved.\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1831, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this ambition\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If people have taken any offense, we are really sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1887, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1841}, {\"ngram\": \"any offense\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oh, the beauties of community tolerance!\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1929, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Oh, the beauties\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1905}, {\"ngram\": \"community tolerance\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Would that the whole world would be tolerant like this!\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 1985, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the whole world\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 1956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the end, sarcasm aside, however you slice the cake, the ceremonies were perverse, with the celebration of drag queens and transgenders and the final scene featuring a throuple (in this case, two men and a woman), apparently ready to do their thing behind closed doors.\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 2258, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 1997}, {\"ngram\": \"the cake\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2040}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremonies\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2056}, {\"ngram\": \"the celebration\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2092}, {\"ngram\": \"drag queens\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2107}, {\"ngram\": \"transgenders\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2124}, {\"ngram\": \"the final scene\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2144}, {\"ngram\": \"a throuple\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2165}, {\"ngram\": \"this case\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2179}, {\"ngram\": \"two men\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2188}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2200}, {\"ngram\": \"their thing\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2237}, {\"ngram\": \"closed doors\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2257}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, this showcased \\\"the vibrant and influential role of the French LGBTQ+ community.\\\"\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2320, \"end\": 2326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999047494607723, \"rank\": 9.525808942064995e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"the vibrant and influential role\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the words of Le Filip, who recently won the \\\"Drag Race France\\\" competition, \\\"The (French) government knows what it's doing.\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2473, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2432, \"end\": 2438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999047494607723, \"rank\": 9.525808942064995e-05, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the words\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2359}, {\"ngram\": \"Le Filip\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2371}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"Drag Race France\\\" competition\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They want to show themselves in the best way possible.\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best way\", \"from\": 2506, \"to\": 2518}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They showed no restraints in expression.\\\"\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2570, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no restraints\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2554}, {\"ngram\": \"expression\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And this leads me to back to my opening question: Why is this the way that France's LGBTQ+ community wants to be seen and known?\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2700, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2647, \"end\": 2653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.7670717448780949, \"rank\": 0.3031927113027359, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my opening question\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2620}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As I have interacted with LGBTQ+ identified individuals over the years, the vast majority of them have been quite normal in terms of their interests and lifestyle.\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2865, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LGBTQ+\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2734}, {\"ngram\": \"individuals\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2757}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 2763, \"to\": 2772}, {\"ngram\": \"the vast majority\", \"from\": 2774, \"to\": 2791}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2831}, {\"ngram\": \"their interests\", \"from\": 2835, \"to\": 2850}, {\"ngram\": \"lifestyle\", \"from\": 2855, \"to\": 2864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are our co-workers, our neighbors, our family members, our friends, working their jobs, having their relationships, some of them raising kids too.\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 3017, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our co\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2881}, {\"ngram\": \"workers\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2889}, {\"ngram\": \"our neighbors\", \"from\": 2891, \"to\": 2904}, {\"ngram\": \"our family members\", \"from\": 2906, \"to\": 2924}, {\"ngram\": \"our friends\", \"from\": 2926, \"to\": 2937}, {\"ngram\": \"their jobs\", \"from\": 2947, \"to\": 2957}, {\"ngram\": \"their relationships\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 2985}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet many that I have interacted with have also had no problem with little children attending absolutely vulgar gay pride events, even with some events featuring public nudity.\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3194, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no problem\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3080}, {\"ngram\": \"little children\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3101}, {\"ngram\": \"absolutely vulgar gay pride events\", \"from\": 3112, \"to\": 3146}, {\"ngram\": \"some events\", \"from\": 3158, \"to\": 3169}, {\"ngram\": \"public nudity\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Something does not add up.\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3221, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Something\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3204}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In my 2011 book A Queer Thing Happened to America, I noted that, \\\"Gay activists are so careful to utilize carefully crafted language to communicate their points, using 'gay' rather than 'homosexual,' speaking of 'gay and lesbian civil rights' rather than a 'gay agenda,' and referring to 'sexual orientation' rather than 'sexual preference,' just to name a few.\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my 2011 book\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3238}, {\"ngram\": \"A Queer Thing\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3252}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3272}, {\"ngram\": \"Gay activists\", \"from\": 3289, \"to\": 3302}, {\"ngram\": \"carefully crafted language\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3355}, {\"ngram\": \"their points\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3383}, {\"ngram\": \"gay\", \"from\": 3392, \"to\": 3395}, {\"ngram\": \"'gay and lesbian civil rights\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3464}, {\"ngram\": \"'sexual orientation' rather than 'sexual preference\", \"from\": 3511, \"to\": 3562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This makes it all the more ironic that such public, self-exposing, and self-denigrating displays have been standard fare in major gay pride events.\\\"\", \"from\": 3585, \"to\": 3733, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such public, self-exposing\", \"from\": 3624, \"to\": 3650}, {\"ngram\": \"self-denigrating displays\", \"from\": 3656, \"to\": 3681}, {\"ngram\": \"standard fare\", \"from\": 3692, \"to\": 3705}, {\"ngram\": \"major gay pride events\", \"from\": 3709, \"to\": 3731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I then quoted lesbian, feminist activist, Tammy Bruce, who said, \\\".\", \"from\": 3735, \"to\": 3802, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3749, \"end\": 3756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lesbian\", \"score\": 0.9982580631857865, \"rank\": 0.0013416678697148593, \"text\": \"lesbian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lesbian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lesbian\"}, {\"begin\": 3777, \"end\": 3788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tammy_Bruce\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tammy Bruce\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tammy_Bruce\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tammy_Bruce\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"feminist activist\", \"from\": 3758, \"to\": 3775}]}, {\"sentence\": \".\", \"from\": 3803, \"to\": 3804, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \".\", \"from\": 3805, \"to\": 3806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"if there is suddenly such a concern within the gay community about appearing 'normal,' perhaps men in suits should replace men in G-strings at gay-pride parades.\\\"\", \"from\": 3807, \"to\": 3969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a concern\", \"from\": 3828, \"to\": 3842}, {\"ngram\": \"the gay community\", \"from\": 3850, \"to\": 3867}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 3902, \"to\": 3905}, {\"ngram\": \"suits\", \"from\": 3909, \"to\": 3914}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 3930, \"to\": 3933}, {\"ngram\": \"G-strings\", \"from\": 3937, \"to\": 3946}, {\"ngram\": \"gay-pride parades\", \"from\": 3950, \"to\": 3967}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bruce then related \\\"I was at an organizing meeting for a gay-pride group that shall remain nameless.\", \"from\": 3971, \"to\": 4071, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bruce\", \"from\": 3971, \"to\": 3976}, {\"ngram\": \"an organizing meeting\", \"from\": 4000, \"to\": 4021}, {\"ngram\": \"a gay-pride group\", \"from\": 4026, \"to\": 4043}, {\"ngram\": \"nameless\", \"from\": 4062, \"to\": 4070}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the bigger arguments at the meeting involved whether or not to have a giant penis on a float, \\u00e1 la the Rose Parade.\", \"from\": 4072, \"to\": 4194, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bigger arguments\", \"from\": 4079, \"to\": 4099}, {\"ngram\": \"the meeting\", \"from\": 4103, \"to\": 4114}, {\"ngram\": \"a giant penis\", \"from\": 4147, \"to\": 4160}, {\"ngram\": \"a float\", \"from\": 4164, \"to\": 4171}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e1\", \"from\": 4173, \"to\": 4174}, {\"ngram\": \"the Rose Parade\", \"from\": 4178, \"to\": 4193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a contentious debate, the Giant Penis Float lost out, but just barely.\", \"from\": 4195, \"to\": 4271, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4233, \"end\": 4238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penis\", \"score\": 0.9998690882675623, \"rank\": 0.0001309288727734024, \"text\": \"Penis\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a contentious debate\", \"from\": 4201, \"to\": 4221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The women in the room were not amused, and a discussion ensued about how negatively the gay community appears to the rest of the country when our ambassadors are men dressed as female high school cheerleaders.\\\"\", \"from\": 4272, \"to\": 4482, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The women\", \"from\": 4272, \"to\": 4281}, {\"ngram\": \"the room\", \"from\": 4285, \"to\": 4293}, {\"ngram\": \"a discussion\", \"from\": 4315, \"to\": 4327}, {\"ngram\": \"the gay community\", \"from\": 4356, \"to\": 4373}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 4385, \"to\": 4393}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 4397, \"to\": 4408}, {\"ngram\": \"our ambassadors\", \"from\": 4414, \"to\": 4429}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4437}, {\"ngram\": \"female high school cheerleaders\", \"from\": 4449, \"to\": 4480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Precisely so.\", \"from\": 4484, \"to\": 4497, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But why, then, are these perversities so regularly celebrated?\", \"from\": 4498, \"to\": 4560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these perversities\", \"from\": 4517, \"to\": 4535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why are these behaviors flaunted?\", \"from\": 4561, \"to\": 4594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these behaviors\", \"from\": 4569, \"to\": 4584}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I continued, \\\"Just think for a moment about how extreme this really is.\", \"from\": 4596, \"to\": 4667, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 4625, \"to\": 4633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If traditional couples came together for a 'Celebration of Marriage' day in a public park, little children from the community would feel welcome, and people would not have to close their eyes and cover their ears to avoid contact with vulgar and obscene images, gestures, and words.\", \"from\": 4668, \"to\": 4950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"traditional couples\", \"from\": 4671, \"to\": 4690}, {\"ngram\": \"Marriage\", \"from\": 4727, \"to\": 4735}, {\"ngram\": \"a public park\", \"from\": 4744, \"to\": 4757}, {\"ngram\": \"little children\", \"from\": 4759, \"to\": 4774}, {\"ngram\": \"the community\", \"from\": 4780, \"to\": 4793}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4818, \"to\": 4824}, {\"ngram\": \"their eyes\", \"from\": 4849, \"to\": 4859}, {\"ngram\": \"their ears\", \"from\": 4870, \"to\": 4880}, {\"ngram\": \"contact\", \"from\": 4890, \"to\": 4897}, {\"ngram\": \"vulgar and obscene images\", \"from\": 4903, \"to\": 4928}, {\"ngram\": \"gestures\", \"from\": 4930, \"to\": 4938}, {\"ngram\": \"words\", \"from\": 4944, \"to\": 4949}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet large gay celebrations worldwide are commonly marked by nude or semi-nude parades, simulated sex acts, and floats with massive, protruding phalluses.\", \"from\": 4951, \"to\": 5104, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"large gay celebrations\", \"from\": 4955, \"to\": 4977}, {\"ngram\": \"nude or semi-nude parades\", \"from\": 5011, \"to\": 5036}, {\"ngram\": \"simulated sex acts\", \"from\": 5038, \"to\": 5056}, {\"ngram\": \"massive, protruding phalluses\", \"from\": 5074, \"to\": 5103}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Is not this perversity rather than diversity?\\\"\", \"from\": 5105, \"to\": 5151, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this perversity\", \"from\": 5112, \"to\": 5127}, {\"ngram\": \"diversity\", \"from\": 5140, \"to\": 5149}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the book, I documented some of the most outrageous expressions as major gay pride events, representing the depths of sexual perversity, then asking if we could imagine any ethnic group engaging in this kind of public celebration.\", \"from\": 5153, \"to\": 5385, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the book\", \"from\": 5156, \"to\": 5164}, {\"ngram\": \"the most outrageous expressions\", \"from\": 5187, \"to\": 5218}, {\"ngram\": \"major gay pride events\", \"from\": 5222, \"to\": 5244}, {\"ngram\": \"the depths\", \"from\": 5259, \"to\": 5269}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual perversity\", \"from\": 5273, \"to\": 5290}, {\"ngram\": \"any ethnic group\", \"from\": 5324, \"to\": 5340}, {\"ngram\": \"this kind\", \"from\": 5353, \"to\": 5362}, {\"ngram\": \"public celebration\", \"from\": 5366, \"to\": 5384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Who in their right mind would associate any of this with Black Pride or Asian Pride or Hispanic Pride or Jewish Pride?\", \"from\": 5386, \"to\": 5504, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5443, \"end\": 5448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_people\", \"score\": 0.9999999948181539, \"rank\": 5.18191907525886e-09, \"text\": \"Black\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Black_people\"}, {\"begin\": 5449, \"end\": 5454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gay_pride\", \"score\": 0.8762040624401861, \"rank\": 0.14128644137383878, \"text\": \"Pride\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gay_pride\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gay_pride\"}, {\"begin\": 5458, \"end\": 5469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_pride\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Asian Pride\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_pride\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_pride\"}, {\"begin\": 5473, \"end\": 5481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hispanic_and_Latino_Americans\", \"score\": 0.9579728745939462, \"rank\": 0.04387089292464856, \"text\": \"Hispanic\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hispanic_and_Latino_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hispanic_and_Latino_Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 5491, \"end\": 5497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judaism\", \"score\": 0.9999391026688899, \"rank\": 6.043833988047614e-05, \"text\": \"Jewish\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judaism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judaism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their right mind\", \"from\": 5393, \"to\": 5409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it is standard fare when it comes to the celebration of LGBTQ+ Pride.\", \"from\": 5505, \"to\": 5578, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"standard fare\", \"from\": 5515, \"to\": 5528}, {\"ngram\": \"the celebration\", \"from\": 5546, \"to\": 5561}, {\"ngram\": \"LGBTQ+ Pride\", \"from\": 5565, \"to\": 5577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why?\", \"from\": 5579, \"to\": 5583, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The answer is that, fundamentally, homosexual relationships and transgender expression represent a violation of God's design for humanity, both in terms of the meaning of marriage and the meaning of sex-gender.\", \"from\": 5585, \"to\": 5795, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The answer\", \"from\": 5585, \"to\": 5595}, {\"ngram\": \"homosexual relationships\", \"from\": 5620, \"to\": 5644}, {\"ngram\": \"transgender expression\", \"from\": 5649, \"to\": 5671}, {\"ngram\": \"a violation\", \"from\": 5682, \"to\": 5693}, {\"ngram\": \"God's design\", \"from\": 5697, \"to\": 5709}, {\"ngram\": \"humanity\", \"from\": 5714, \"to\": 5722}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 5732, \"to\": 5737}, {\"ngram\": \"the meaning\", \"from\": 5741, \"to\": 5752}, {\"ngram\": \"marriage\", \"from\": 5756, \"to\": 5764}, {\"ngram\": \"the meaning\", \"from\": 5769, \"to\": 5780}, {\"ngram\": \"sex-gender\", \"from\": 5784, \"to\": 5794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the end, regardless of the degree to which every gay or lesbian or trans person on the planet is a fellow human being, created in the image of God and the object of His love, there is something fundamentally amiss with their desires and expression.\", \"from\": 5797, \"to\": 6048, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 5800, \"to\": 5807}, {\"ngram\": \"the degree\", \"from\": 5823, \"to\": 5833}, {\"ngram\": \"the planet\", \"from\": 5883, \"to\": 5893}, {\"ngram\": \"a fellow human being\", \"from\": 5897, \"to\": 5917}, {\"ngram\": \"the image\", \"from\": 5930, \"to\": 5939}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 5943, \"to\": 5946}, {\"ngram\": \"the object\", \"from\": 5951, \"to\": 5961}, {\"ngram\": \"His love\", \"from\": 5965, \"to\": 5973}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 5984, \"to\": 5993}, {\"ngram\": \"their desires\", \"from\": 6019, \"to\": 6032}, {\"ngram\": \"expression\", \"from\": 6037, \"to\": 6047}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In short, this comes down to a sexual deviation, expressed either in same-sex attraction or a confused gender identity (and in writing this, I recognize that in the overwhelming majority of cases, this deviation was not asked for or desired).\", \"from\": 6049, \"to\": 6291, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sexual deviation\", \"from\": 6078, \"to\": 6096}, {\"ngram\": \"same-sex attraction\", \"from\": 6118, \"to\": 6137}, {\"ngram\": \"a confused gender identity\", \"from\": 6141, \"to\": 6167}, {\"ngram\": \"the overwhelming majority\", \"from\": 6210, \"to\": 6235}, {\"ngram\": \"cases\", \"from\": 6239, \"to\": 6244}, {\"ngram\": \"this deviation\", \"from\": 6246, \"to\": 6260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When this deviation is celebrated, it brings the perversions to the surface, also providing fertile ground for satanic expressions.\", \"from\": 6293, \"to\": 6424, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this deviation\", \"from\": 6298, \"to\": 6312}, {\"ngram\": \"the perversions\", \"from\": 6338, \"to\": 6353}, {\"ngram\": \"the surface\", \"from\": 6357, \"to\": 6368}, {\"ngram\": \"fertile ground\", \"from\": 6385, \"to\": 6399}, {\"ngram\": \"satanic expressions\", \"from\": 6404, \"to\": 6423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These would include a devil-horned drag queen reading to little children, celebrated on Pride.com with the caption, \\\"This Drag Queen Dressed as a Satanic Goddess to Read to Kids\\\" in honor of LGBT History Month and Halloween.\", \"from\": 6425, \"to\": 6649, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6513, \"end\": 6522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Here_Media\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pride.com\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Here_Media\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Here_Media\"}, {\"begin\": 6616, \"end\": 6634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT_History_Month\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LGBT History Month\", \"types\": [\"Q1445650\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT_History_Month\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT_History_Month\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"little children\", \"from\": 6482, \"to\": 6497}, {\"ngram\": \"the caption\", \"from\": 6528, \"to\": 6539}, {\"ngram\": \"This Drag Queen\", \"from\": 6542, \"to\": 6557}, {\"ngram\": \"a Satanic Goddess\", \"from\": 6569, \"to\": 6586}, {\"ngram\": \"Kids\", \"from\": 6598, \"to\": 6602}, {\"ngram\": \"honor\", \"from\": 6607, \"to\": 6612}, {\"ngram\": \"Halloween\", \"from\": 6639, \"to\": 6648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We can now add to this list the Paris 2024 opening ceremonies, now declaring to the entire world the fundamentally disordered nature of all sexualities and expressions that deviate from God's original design.\", \"from\": 6651, \"to\": 6859, \"entities\": [{\"b